                "track": "physical",
                "frequency": "1/day",
                "effect": "At the debilitated state, the victim becomes partially vaporous. Attacks made by or targeting the victim have a 25% miss chance. At bedridden, this effect ends and the victim is incorporeal. At dead, the victim\u2019s form completely dissipates into fine particles.",
